author: @rafamarxxx
content: OMG! So happy you enjoyed your stay in Brazil! I'm brazilian and I lived in Rio for a short period of time, so it was really heartwarming watching this vlog. I wish I went to the concert so I could say hi ^^. Wishing you a great trip back home.
